NORTH ATLANTIC.
BERMUDA TO AZORES OR IRELAND.
1. 36 FOOT S/V GOLDEN EAGLE, WHITE HULL WITH BLUE STRIPE,
   TWO PERSONS ON BOARD, OVERDUE BERMUDA TO AZORES
   OR IRELAND. VESSELS IN VICINITY REQUESTED TO KEEP
   A SHARP LOOKOUT, ASSIST IF POSSIBLE. REPORTS TO
   MRCC DUBLIN OR MRSC VALENTIA, PHONE: 35 36 6947 6109,
   E-MAIL: MRSCVALENTIA@TRANSPORT.IE.
2. CANCEL HYDROLANT 1502/11.
